<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter is-resized"><img loading="lazy" src="/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/titulo.gif" alt="" class="wp-image-61" width="574" height="431"/></figure></div>



<p>For who haven&#8217;t played BrazSonic 1, it is avaliable for download on this website. BrazSonic 1 was released on 2004 for Windows.</p>



<p>BrazSonic, the &#8220;national hedgehog&#8221;, was developed in few months using Game Maker 5.3 on that time, a well used Windows gamedev tool with many possibilities.</p>



<ul class="wp-block-gallery columns-3 is-cropped"><li class="blocks-gallery-item"><figure><a href="/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/shot0085.jpg" data-rel="lightbox-image-0" data-rl_title="bs1 - intro" data-rl_caption="" title="bs1 - intro"><img loading="lazy" width="320" height="242" src="/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/shot0085.jpg" alt="bs1 - intro" data-id="117" data-link="/shot0085/" class="wp-image-117" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/shot0085.jpg 320w, /wp-content/uploads/2019/01/shot0085-300x227.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px" /></a></figure></li><li class="blocks-gallery-item"><figure><a href="/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/brasonicfull_04.jpg" data-rel="lightbox-image-1" data-rl_title="bs1 - sampa 3" data-rl_caption="" title="bs1 - sampa 3"><img loading="lazy" width="800" height="600" src="/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/brasonicfull_04.jpg" alt="bs1 - sampa 3" data-id="109" data-link="/brasonic1/attachment/brasonicfull_04/" class="wp-image-109" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/brasonicfull_04.jpg 800w, /wp-content/uploads/2019/01/brasonicfull_04-300x225.jpg 300w, /wp-content/uploads/2019/01/brasonicfull_04-768x576.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /></a></figure></li><li class="blocks-gallery-item"><figure><a href="/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/brasonicfull_08.jpg" data-rel="lightbox-image-2" data-rl_title="bs1 - multiplayer" data-rl_caption="" title="bs1 - multiplayer"><img loading="lazy" width="600" height="450" src="/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/brasonicfull_08.jpg" alt="bs1 - multiplayer" data-id="110" data-link="/brasonic1/attachment/brasonicfull_08/" class="wp-image-110" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/brasonicfull_08.jpg 600w, /wp-content/uploads/2019/01/brasonicfull_08-300x225.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /></a></figure></li><li class="blocks-gallery-item"><figure><a href="/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/bs1_lula.jpg" data-rel="lightbox-image-3" data-rl_title="bs1 - luça" data-rl_caption="" title="bs1 - luça"><img loading="lazy" width="400" height="300" src="/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/bs1_lula.jpg" alt="bs1 - luça" data-id="102" data-link="/bs1_lula/" class="wp-image-102" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/bs1_lula.jpg 400w, /wp-content/uploads/2019/01/bs1_lula-300x225.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" /></a></figure></li><li class="blocks-gallery-item"><figure><a href="/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/P00002030.jpg" data-rel="lightbox-image-4" data-rl_title="bs1 - amazone" data-rl_caption="" title="bs1 - amazone"><img loading="lazy" width="400" height="300" src="/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/P00002030.jpg" alt="bs1 - amazone" data-id="104" data-link="/p00002030/" class="wp-image-104" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/P00002030.jpg 400w, /wp-content/uploads/2019/01/P00002030-300x225.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" /></a></figure></li><li class="blocks-gallery-item"><figure><a href="/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/brazone.jpg" data-rel="lightbox-image-5" data-rl_title="bs1 - brasilia" data-rl_caption="" title="bs1 - brasilia"><img loading="lazy" width="319" height="239" src="/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/brazone.jpg" alt="bs1 - brasilia" data-id="101" data-link="/brazone/" class="wp-image-101" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/brazone.jpg 319w, /wp-content/uploads/2019/01/brazone-300x225.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 319px) 100vw, 319px" /></a></figure></li></ul>



<p>The 00s Sonic the Hedgehog online communities, such as Power Sonic Forum, Portal Sonic and Sonic Fangames HQ were very important for this game divulgation and feedback.</p>



<p>The game reception were considerably good, with hundreds of thousands downloads and also acknowledgment of some internet portals.</p>



<p>Despite being a &#8220;little outdated&#8221;, BrazSonic 1 will be avaliable for download anytime.<a href="/en/brazsonic1/"> Check it out for info and download</a>.</p>



<p>Some years after, as an attempt to build a legacy for BrazSonic, I started a sequel project which failed after some years of work. Although BrazSonic is finally back on <a href="/en/brasonic20xx/">a &#8220;new&#8221; and better game</a>.</p>
